name: Open Invoices by Payment Block (Top-10)
query:
SELECT 
"Last Inv. Item Payment Block Key"  AS "Payment Block"
,COUNT(case_id) AS "No. of Invoices"
,SUM ("Inv. Converted USD Amount") AS "Invoice Amount in $"
FROM "defaultview-225"
WHERE   "Last Inv. Item Clearing Date" IS NULL
  AND "Last Inv. Item Payment Block Key" IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 3 DESC
LIMIT 10
description: Overview of Top-10 Open Overdue Invoices, grouped by Payment Block and sorted by Number of Invoices
signalFragment:
SELECT 
"Last Inv. Item Payment Block Key"  AS "Payment Block"
,COUNT(case_id) AS "No. of Invoices"
,SUM ("Inv. Converted USD Amount") AS "Invoice Amount in $"
FROM "THIS_PROCESS"
WHERE   "Last Inv. Item Clearing Date" IS NULL
  AND "Last Inv. Item Payment Block Key" IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 3 DESC
LIMIT 10
